name: Where do you go? (Community Game Jam)
name_original: Where do you go? (Community Game Jam)
description:
This is my current Prototype for the Game Jam: Community Game Jam.

I'm really enjoying this Task. This is my first attempt for a game and I'm really happy about it. So a BIG Thank you to all Youtuber/Creators of the GameJam!:CodeMyst, Sykoo, Blackthornprod Games, Dani, Brackeys, AquaXV, Yilian, TheDutchMagikarp, Duxez

If you want to download the Game prototype (ask me) too give me a small Feedback I would be very happy!

See you!
